    "title": "InVideo AI Tutorial: Create Stunning Videos from a Prompt",
    "excerpt": "Step-by-step InVideo AI tutorial: go from a text prompt to a polished YouTube video, ad, or clip in minutes. No editing skills needed. Start free today.",
