      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of video tools over the past two years. Most of them promise the world and deliver a clunky timeline that takes hours to figure out. InVideo AI is different — and I mean genuinely, noticeably different. You type what you want, and it builds the video for you. Script, voiceover, subtitles, b-roll, transitions — all of it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This tutorial walks you through the entire process, from zero to a finished video you can upload or run as an ad. Whether you've never opened an editing app or you're a seasoned creator looking to speed up production, you'll find something useful here.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's get into it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is InVideo AI and Why Should You Care?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "InVideo AI is a web-based platform that turns a simple text prompt into a complete video. No timeline scrubbing. No stock footage hunting. No hiring a voice actor. You describe what you want — a 60-second Instagram Reel about productivity hacks, a 10-minute YouTube explainer on quantum computing, a 15-second ad for a SaaS product — and the AI handles the rest.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
