            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://invideo.sjv.io/c/6249333/883681/12258"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform lives at ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "invideo.io",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and runs entirely in your browser. That means no downloads, no \"your GPU isn't supported\" errors, and no waiting for a massive file to render locally. Everything processes on their servers, and you export a finished MP4 when you're done.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
