            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What sets InVideo AI apart from other AI video generators is the combination of models it gives you access to: Seedance 2.0, Veo 3.1, and Kling 3. These aren't marketing buzzwords — they're the engines that generate realistic motion, smooth transitions, and context-aware visuals. The result? Videos that don't look like a robot slapped them together.",
