        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Specific prompt:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " \"Create a 3-minute YouTube video about 5 science-backed morning routines for productivity. Use a male voiceover, upbeat background music, subtitle text on screen, and modern b-roll of someone stretching, journaling, and making coffee.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The specific prompt will get you closer to what you imagined on the first try. But even the vague one produces something usable — InVideo AI is surprisingly good at inferring context.",
