        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After you submit your prompt, InVideo AI gets to work. You'll see a script being generated in real time, followed by scene-by-scene assembly. The AI selects stock footage, generates or selects a voiceover, adds subtitles, and layers in music.",
            "marks": []
