      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The first time I did this, I expected something rough — a skeleton I'd need to polish for an hour. Instead, I got a video that was 85% ready to publish. The footage matched the script, the voiceover sounded natural (not that robotic monotone you hear in cheap tools), and the subtitles were properly timed.",
